premise_source_doc_sentence: Anni-Frid Synni , Princess Reuss of Plauen  (  Anni-Frid Synni , Prinzessin Reuss von Plauen born Anni-Frid Synni Lyngstad , -LSB- ² ɑnːɪˌfriːd ˈlʏŋstɑ -RSB- ; -LSB- ² anːɪˌfriːd ˈlʏŋstɑːd -RSB- , 15 November 1945  )  , widely known as Frida Lyngstad or by just the mononym Frida  (  -LSB- ² friːdɑ -RSB- ; -LSB- ² friːda -RSB-  )  , is a Swedish pop and jazz singer .
